definitions.definition: A racquet sport resembling tennis , played with solid paddles and a perforated ball, which combines elements of badminton , table tennis and wiffleball .
The ball used in the sport of pickleball.

main_definition: ( uncountable ) A racquet sport resembling tennis , played with solid paddles and a perforated ball, which combines elements of badminton , table tennis and wiffleball .
secondary_definitions: ( countable ) The ball used in the sport of pickleball.
